  "description": "A stunning landscape photograph captures a majestic mountain peak rising dramatically against a backdrop of fluffy white clouds and a pale blue sky. The mountain is characterized by its smooth, rounded granite face, typical of glacial formations. Evergreen trees of varying heights densely cover the lower slopes and foreground, creating a lush contrast with the stark rock face. A faint, wispy waterfall descends the mountainside, adding to the scene's dynamic quality. The lighting is soft and diffused, suggesting a slightly overcast day.",
